Description:
    Adds the necessary models, specs and migrations and configurations to your app so that it 
    can use the slimcore_authorizer engine.

Example:
    ./script/generate slimcore_authorizer

    This will create:
        app/models/user_profile.rb
        app/models/lab_group_profile.rb
	app/views/user_profiles/_form.html.erb
	app/views/lab_group_profiles/_form.html.erb
        config/application.yml
        config/initializers/1-load_application_config.rb
        config/initializers/cas_server.rb
        db/migrations/TIMESTAMP_add_slimcore_authorizer.rb
	public/stylesheets/tinytable.css
	public/javascripts/tinytable-packed.js
	public/images/asc.gif
	public/images/bg.gif
	public/images/desc.gif
	public/images/first.gif
	public/images/header-bg.gif
	public/images/header-selected-bg.gif
	public/images/last.gif
	public/images/next.gif
	public/images/previous.gif
	public/images/sort.gif
        spec/models/user_profile_spec.rb
        spec/models/lab_group_profile_spec.rb        
